    <section class="mb-16">
     <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ“</span> Ukuran Pemusatan Data</h2>
     <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6"><!-- Mean -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-indigo-500">
       <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
        ğŸ“
       </div>
       <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Mean (Rata-rata)</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Jumlah semua data dibagi banyaknya data. Paling sering digunakan!</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-center font-mono text-lg">xÌ„ = Î£xáµ¢ / n</p>
       </div>
       <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-700"><strong>Contoh:</strong> Nilai 7, 8, 9<br>
          Mean = (7+8+9)/3 = <strong>8</strong></p>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Median -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-purple-500">
       <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
        ğŸ¯
       </div>
       <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Median (Nilai Tengah)</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Nilai yang membagi data menjadi dua bagian sama besar setelah diurutkan.</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-center text-sm"><strong>n ganjil:</strong> Data ke-(n+1)/2<br><strong>n genap:</strong> Rata-rata 2 data tengah</p>
       </div>
       <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-purple-700"><strong>Contoh:</strong> 5, 7, <u>8</u>, 9, 10<br>
          Median = <strong>8</strong></p>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Modus -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-pink-500">
       <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
        ğŸ†
       </div>
       <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Modus (Nilai Terbanyak)</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Nilai yang paling sering muncul dalam data. Bisa lebih dari satu!</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-center text-sm">Cari nilai dengan<br>
         frekuensi tertinggi</p>
       </div>
       <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-pink-50 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-pink-700"><strong>Contoh:</strong> 5, <strong>7</strong>, <strong>7</strong>, 8, <strong>7</strong>, 9<br>
          Modus = <strong>7</strong> (muncul 3x)</p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </section><!-- Ukuran Penyebaran -->
    <section class="mb-16">
     <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ“</span> Ukuran Penyebaran Data</h2>
     <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><!-- Jangkauan -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><span class="text-3xl">â†”ï¸</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Jangkauan (Range)</h3>
       </div>
       <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Selisih antara nilai terbesar dan terkecil. Ukuran penyebaran paling sederhana!</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-center font-mono text-lg">R = X<sub>maks</sub> - X<sub>min</sub></p>
       </div>
       <div class="example-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-green-800"><strong>ğŸ›’ Contoh Nyata:</strong> Harga cabai di 5 pasar: Rp25.000, Rp28.000, Rp30.000, Rp32.000, Rp35.000<br>
          Jangkauan = 35.000 - 25.000 = <strong>Rp10.000</strong></p>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Simpangan Rata-rata -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ“Š</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Simpangan Rata-rata</h3>
       </div>
       <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Rata-rata dari selisih mutlak setiap data dengan mean.</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-center font-mono">SR = Î£|xáµ¢ - xÌ„| / n</p>
       </div>
       <div class="example-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-green-800"><strong>ğŸ“ Contoh Nyata:</strong> Nilai ulangan: 6, 7, 8, 9, 10 (Mean = 8)<br>
          SR = (|6-8|+|7-8|+|8-8|+|9-8|+|10-8|)/5 = 6/5 = <strong>1,2</strong></p>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Ragam/Variansi -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ”¢</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Ragam (Variansi)</h3>
       </div>
       <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Rata-rata dari kuadrat selisih setiap data dengan mean.</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-center font-mono">SÂ² = Î£(xáµ¢ - xÌ„)Â² / n</p>
       </div>
       <div class="tip-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800"><strong>ğŸ’¡ Catatan:</strong> Variansi menggunakan kuadrat agar selisih negatif dan positif tidak saling menghilangkan!</p>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Simpangan Baku -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 card-hover">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ“ˆ</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Simpangan Baku (Std Dev)</h3>
       </div>
       <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Akar kuadrat dari variansi. Ukuran penyebaran paling populer!</p>
       <div class="formula-box p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-center font-mono">S = âˆš(Î£(xáµ¢ - xÌ„)Â² / n)</p>
       </div>
       <div class="tip-box p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800"><strong>ğŸ’¡ Keunggulan:</strong> Satuannya sama dengan data asli, berbeda dengan variansi yang satuannya kuadrat.</p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </section><!-- Contoh Soal Section -->
