           <h4 class="font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">ğŸ“ Penyelesaian Mean:</h4>
           <p class="text-gray-700">xÌ„ = (15 + 18 + 20 + 22 + 17 + 19 + 23) / 7<br>
             xÌ„ = 134 / 7<br><strong>xÌ„ = 19,14 pelanggan</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border-l-4 border-purple-500">
           <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">ğŸ“ Penyelesaian Median:</h4>
           <p class="text-gray-700">1. Urutkan data: 15, 17, 18, <u>19</u>, 20, 22, 23<br>
             2. n = 7 (ganjil), maka median = data ke-(7+1)/2 = data ke-4<br><strong>Median = 19 pelanggan</strong></p>
