           <p class="text-gray-700">Hitung frekuensi:<br>
             â€¢ 38 â†’ 2 kali<br>
             â€¢ 39 â†’ 1 kali<br>
             â€¢ <strong>40 â†’ 4 kali</strong> â† terbanyak!<br>
             â€¢ 41 â†’ 1 kali<br>
             â€¢ 42 â†’ 2 kali<br><strong>Modus = 40</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border-l-4 border-green-500">
           <h4 class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">ğŸ“ Penyelesaian Jangkauan:</h4>
