     <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-3xl">ğŸ’¡</span> Tips &amp; Trik Menjawab Soal</h2>
     <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-yellow-200">
       <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-orange-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><span>ğŸ¯</span> Trik Cepat Mean</h3>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">1.</span> <span>Jika data berurutan dengan selisih sama (deret aritmatika), <strong>mean = (data pertama + data terakhir) / 2</strong></span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">2.</span> <span>Gunakan kalkulator untuk data banyak, jangan hitung manual!</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">3.</span> <span>Perkirakan dulu jawabannya untuk cek perhitungan</span></li>
       </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-green-200">
       <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-green-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><span>ğŸ“</span> Trik Cepat Median</h3>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">1.</span> <span><strong>SELALU urutkan data terlebih dahulu!</strong> Ini langkah wajib.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">2.</span> <span>n ganjil: ambil data tengah langsung</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">3.</span> <span>n genap: rata-ratakan 2 data tengah</span></li>
       </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-purple-200">
       <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-purple-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><span>ğŸ”¢</span> Trik Variansi &amp; Simpangan Baku</h3>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-500 font-bold">1.</span> <span>Buat tabel untuk menghitung sistematis: xáµ¢ | xáµ¢-xÌ„ | (xáµ¢-xÌ„)Â²</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-500 font-bold">2.</span> <span>Î£(xáµ¢-xÌ„) <strong>SELALU = 0</strong> (untuk cek perhitungan)</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-500 font-bold">3.</span> <span>Simpangan baku = âˆšVariansi (jangan lupa akar!)</span></li>
       </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-blue-200">
       <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><span>âš¡</span> Trik Umum</h3>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">1.</span> <span><strong>Simpangan baku kecil</strong> = data konsisten/seragam</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">2.</span> <span><strong>Simpangan baku besar</strong> = data bervariasi/tersebar</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">3.</span> <span>Bandingkan simpangan baku, bukan variansi (satuannya beda!)</span></li>
       </ul>
      </div>
     </div><!-- Rumus Ringkas -->
     <div class="mt-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><span>ğŸ“‹</span> Ringkasan Rumus</h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
       <div class="p-4 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-1">Mean</p>
        <p class="font-mono">xÌ„ = Î£xáµ¢ / n</p>
       </div>
       <div class="p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="font-bold text-purple-600 mb-1">Median (n ganjil)</p>
        <p class="font-mono">X<sub>(n+1)/2</sub></p>
       </div>
       <div class="p-4 bg-pink-50 rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">Modus</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Nilai frekuensi terbanyak</p>
       </div>
